                    <li>
                        After receipt of complaints from the customer, marketing officer shall acknowledge the same & details of the same shall be recorded in customer complaint register, no. FMK04.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Incase complaint is commercial, i.e. related to rates, delivery, excise matter, taxes, quantity, etc. marketing officer shall analyze the same and decide necessary actions in consultation with PARTNER.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Incase complaints is technical…
                    </li>
                    <br />
                    <ol>
                        <li>Marketing officer shall record the details in corrective action report, form no. F MR 08 and hand over to Proprietor.</li>
                        <li>PARTNER &nbsp; shall carryout the analysis and mentions the result in corrective action report, form no. F MR 08. </li>
                        <li>Based on the analysis, investigate the causes and decide the corrective action needed to eliminate the cause of non-conformity in corrective action report, form no. F MR 08 and send one copy of the same to marketing officer. Accordingly marketing officer shall give the feedback to customer.  </li>
                        <li>PARTNER &nbsp; shall make arrangement to implement the decided action and verify the results. The record of implementation & verification shall be recorded in corrective action report, form no. F MR 08. If required by the customer, the same shall be informed.  </li>
